{"tid":520722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[炒賣日本福袋]中國人想做的事，沒有人能夠阻止","createTime":"2018-01-05T16:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T12:02:52.000Z","uid":41818,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f7485e2fe5792ee9fc400d04db0cb17b7200fe4f","tid":520722,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/jlr0V0V2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2Fjlr0V0V2.png&h=6ea78ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人不時都上日本新聞節目，日本人對他們的好感度不斷下降。最近，他們轉賣福袋的事情上了新聞，令其他排隊買福袋的日本客人非常不爽。朝日電視台的晨間節目《モーニングショー》，在12月31日晚上派攝製隊去拍攝大型電器店的福袋隊列。雖然只是晚上十時，但已經有大批人到場排隊，希望可以買到願望清單上的福袋。根據攝製隊的說法，在場有不少人都像中國人。<br />\n<br />\n當福袋開賣之後，部份買到福袋的人跟隨門外的疑似中國人的指示，走到停車場進行交易。他們在停車場大概有四輛車，全部都裝滿大型電器店鋪的福袋。攝製隊嘗試向他們進行採訪，但有些人說「這是替朋友買的，他們現在走開了，很快會回來。」，又有些人大吼「很吵啊！這些都是買給自己的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/ca0uIRHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2Fca0uIRHM.png&h=2350f77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/8CimZlkv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2F8CimZlkv.png&h=f9c94e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來，節目工作人員在網上發現，中國網站有招聘告示「1月1日在新宿排隊的工作」，報酬有5000円以上，並會採用50人以上。而且，他們在中國購物網站上，找到店家以6萬8000円賣出價值6萬円的福袋。更誇張的是，他們聲稱存庫達約1300個。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/r7ULorrX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2Fr7ULorrX.png&h=356c6569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/jBjbzRln.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2FjBjbzRln.png&h=b61e7335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/Yh7g3KJ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2FYh7g3KJ9.png&h=7a24b67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪的本地客人指，如果是以轉售為目的而來，希望他們不要再來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201801/kBIEI8ZP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201801%2FkBIEI8ZP.png&h=d7d9fc22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位女士對於中國人來大手入貨感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得買唔到福袋既日本人好慘，但其實真係無咩可以做到。已經限定一人買一個，都仲可以請人黎排隊，真係好佩服呢班中國人啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=6765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6765&d=vVr%2FWdiuJrFGz5lifNlARYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5c8b4ed0\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=6765</a>"},{"pid":"40290322fe3c95aa94dc6a516d56c703788ac598","tid":520722,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:00:31.000Z","msg":"全世界都憎"},{"pid":"d4027885eb5349c8457f29dab0b9a62a7c1cb81a","tid":520722,"uid":43189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:59:41.000Z","msg":"唯一可以做都係擺網上預約，之後落舖頭攞貨<br />\n只限日本ip 購買"},{"pid":"5a666db84ab8c4c9a49d69c7617bfdd7e1bf435c","tid":520722,"uid":31371,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T18:12:12.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 好多日本人都拎黎炒<br />\n...大陸人都仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea0c456ca3ad11afa41b6fa09fe2e69b6f283cc","tid":520722,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4027885eb5349c8457f29dab0b9a62a7c1cb81a","tid":520722,"uid":43189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T17:59:41.000Z","msg":"唯一可以做都係擺網上預約，之後落舖頭攞貨<br />\n只限日本ip 購買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"聽講好多在日支那人香港人收錢做"},{"pid":"c7c7b6b0e5f875a83a98dbb42d9f4aacb45de93c","tid":520722,"uid":31371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cea0c456ca3ad11afa41b6fa09fe2e69b6f283cc","tid":520722,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4027885eb5349c8457f29dab0b9a62a7c1cb81a","tid":520722,"uid":43189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201